  ('pukao-7c4986e7-moex-00039', 'pukao-7c4986e7', 'pukao-7c4986e7-moex-114-6948958a', 'sub-pukao-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種效果，不是造成「總合需求線為負斜率」的原因？', '["價格下降時，民眾的實質財富增加，進而增加消費與總合需求", "價格下降時，利率降低，進而增加投資與總合需求", "價格下降時，國內貨幣貶值，進而增加淨出口與總合需求", "價格下降時，政府支出增加可以提振景氣，刺激總合需求"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7f60f8d3aafd", "answer_pdf_sha1": "79d6a424ea53", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114080", "c": "414", "s": "0709", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-7c4986e7-moex-00040', 'pukao-7c4986e7', 'pukao-7c4986e7-moex-114-6948958a', 'sub-pukao-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設A廠商未投入勞動力時，產量為0；若此廠商僱用6單位勞動力時，產量為90單位，總固定成本為 6元，每一單位勞動的總變動成本為10元。另假設第7單位的勞動邊際產量為4單位，則此廠商僱用7單 位勞動力的總成本為何？', '["66元", "76元", "906元", "946元"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7f60f8d3aafd", "answer_pdf_sha1": "79d6a424ea53", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114080", "c": "414", "s": "0709", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-7c4986e7-moex-00041', 'pukao-7c4986e7', 'pukao-7c4986e7-moex-114-6948958a', 'sub-pukao-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '如果一廠商的生產函數為Q=2K+5L，K和L分別為生產所需的資本和勞動力；已知資本和勞動的價格分 別為r=3、w=4。為使生產成本極小，廠商會使用何種要素？', '["只使用資本", "只使用勞動力", "兩種要素皆使用", "兩種要素皆不使用"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7f60f8d3aafd", "answer_pdf_sha1": "79d6a424ea53", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114080", "c": "414", "s": "0709", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
